text: This is a Glossary of Shinto. Covering different terms used in the religion * Jingu a major Shinto shrine related to the Japanese royal family * Jinja the word for Shinto shrines * Kami no Michi the kunyomi of Shinto * Omiki a sacrifice of alcohol * Shinto the way of the gods * Taisha a major Shinto shrine Category:Shinto
title: Glossary of Shinto
